OL,3,CSouth Africa's ruling ANC party risks
OL,4,Closing its decades-long grip on power
OL,6,FSouth Africa is set to go to the polls
OL,7,Ffor the most unpredictable election in
OL,8,Fthe country's 30 years of democratic
OL,9,Frule, ITV News Global Security Editor
OL,10,FRohit Kachroo reports
OL,12,FRats scurry and sewage water trickles
OL,13,Fpast the ramshackle huts, which are
OL,14,Fhome to tens of thousands of people in
OL,15,Fthe township of Alexandra in
OL,17,F"There's no water at all. There's no
OL,18,Ftoilet, there's no electricity,
OL,19,Fthere's nothing," Pamela Nhobela, who
OL,20,Fhas lived in the same shack for 12
OL,21,Fyears, tells me.
