OL,6,F"My life is not worth living here.
OL,7,FIt's like living in a graveyard. We
OL,8,Flive with rats and the environment is
OL,9,Fnot good. There's nothing good about
OL,10,Fthis area, nothing at all."
OL,12,FAs she leads us towards her home, past
OL,13,Fneighbours wearing T-shirts bearing
OL,14,Fthe logo of the African National
OL,15,FCongress (ANC), the party of
OL,16,Fgovernment ever since the birth of
OL,17,Fdemocracy, she says she "cannot feel
OL,18,Fany love for a party which does not
OL,19,Flove her".
