OL,6,FShe admits to a growing sense of shame
OL,7,Fas we inch closer towards her tinned-
OL,8,Froof squatter shanty, where we will
OL,9,Fsee the place she is forced to call
OL,10,Fhome.
OL,12,F"This is my shack, this is where I
OL,13,Flive. Just look at it. They expect me
OL,14,Fto go and vote for this?"
OL,16,FIt has been 30 years since the
OL,17,Feuphoria of April 27, 1994 - or
OL,18,F"Freedom Day" - when democratic South
OL,19,FAfrica was born.
