OL,3,CSouth Africa's ruling ANC party risks
OL,4,Closing its decades-long grip on power
OL,6,FThis week, its people go to the polls
OL,7,Fagain. But to Pamela, and for many
OL,8,Fpeople in the Alexandra township,
OL,9,Fdemocracy now feels like a draining
OL,10,Fdisappointment.
OL,12,F"The government we've been voting for
OL,13,Fis not helping us, so it's not worth
OL,14,Fit for me to vote," she says.
OL,16,F"How can I vote for someone who is
OL,17,Fgoing to be on top of the world while
OL,18,FI am down here struggling and
OL,19,Fsuffering? I keep on voting, but it's
OL,20,Ffor nothing. There's no change so I'm
OL,21,Fnot going to vote this time."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/18
