OL,6,FSupport for the ANC has fallen because
OL,7,Fof so-called "service delivery
OL,8,Fproblems" - widespread cuts to water
OL,9,Fand electricity supplies, corruption
OL,10,Fand poverty.
OL,12,FThe electricity poles in her community
OL,13,Fhave become a symbol of promises
OL,14,Fundelivered. Because although they
OL,15,Fhaven't carried a regular power supply
OL,16,Ffor as long as anyone can remember,
OL,17,Fthey remain a plaster board for the
OL,18,Fpolitical parties.
