OL,6,FIt is where posters are hung showing
OL,7,Fpictures of their smiling candidates
OL,8,Fpledging a better life.
OL,10,FAnd goading the Alexandrans from
OL,11,Facross the motorway are the gleaming
OL,12,Fskyscrapers of Sandton, the richest
OL,13,Fsquare mile in the country.
OL,15,FEvery morning, minibuses pick people
OL,16,Fup to be taken to cook and clean there
OL,17,F- the business district provides some
OL,18,Fpeople in the township with work, but
OL,19,Funemployment is thought to be in
OL,20,Fexcess of 50 percent.
