OL,3,CSouth Africa's ruling ANC party risks
OL,4,Closing its decades-long grip on power
OL,6,FSouth Africa was meant to embody the
OL,7,Faspirations of the developing world -
OL,8,Fbut the promise of equality upon which
OL,9,Fthe Rainbow Nation was founded has
OL,10,Fcome to feel like a mirage.
OL,12,FThe national unemployment rate rose to
OL,13,F32.9% during the first three months of
OL,14,Fthis year.
