OL,3,CSouth Africa's ruling ANC party risks
OL,4,Closing its decades-long grip on power
OL,6,FThe country remains the most unequal
OL,7,Fin the world and "race remains a key
OL,8,Fdriver" behind the gap, according to a
OL,9,F2022 World Bank report. It found that
OL,10,Fthe richest 10% of the population owns
OL,11,Fmore than four-fifths of financial
OL,12,Fassets.
OL,14,FFor Dr Mamphela Ramphele, the anti-
OL,15,Fapartheid icon, the ANC is a "criminal
OL,16,Fenterprise" which has deceived its
OL,17,Fsupporters to enrich themselves,
OL,18,Fhanding lucrative government contracts
OL,19,Fto friends while doing little to
OL,20,Fimprove the lives of ordinary people.
