OL,6,F"Betrayal doesn't begin to capture the
OL,7,Factual pain, because not only have
OL,8,Fthey betrayed me but particularly,
OL,9,Fthey have betrayed my peers who in the
OL,10,Fend made the ultimate sacrifice," Dr
OL,11,FRamphele says.
OL,13,F"I have come to the sad conclusion, as
OL,14,FArchbishop (Desmond Tutu) did, that
OL,15,Fthe ANC no longer represents the
OL,16,Fpeople of South Africa and their
OL,17,Fdreams. They represent themselves, and
OL,18,Fthemselves, and themselves."
