OL,6,FDr Ramphele was the partner of Steve
OL,7,FBiko, a leading anti-apartheid
OL,8,Factivist who died in custody in 1977
OL,9,Fand who might have become the first
OL,10,Fblack president of South Africa.
OL,12,F"This ANC government for decades has
OL,13,Frefused to teach civil education in
OL,14,Fthe classroom and so they are
OL,15,Fperpetuating a colonial mindset, they
OL,16,Fare perpetuating dependency. They are
OL,17,Fdenying us the ability to be licensed
OL,18,Fdrivers of this beautiful country,
OL,19,Fthis beautiful constitutional
OL,20,Fdemocracy."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/18
