OL,6,F"A grievous error, a grievous
OL,7,Fbetrayal, has been committed by the
OL,8,Fcurrent government and its
OL,9,Fpredecessors. So it is time for every
OL,10,FSouth African to stop complaining and
OL,11,Fexercise the power they have. "
OL,13,FSome polls have suggested that the ANC
OL,14,Fcould score less than 50 percent of
OL,15,Fthe vote, which might force it into a
OL,16,Fshaky coalition with a smaller party
OL,17,Fsuch as the Marxist party, the
OL,18,FEconomic Freedom Fighters.
