OL,6,FWearing a Bafana Bafana shirt, their
OL,7,Fshy son Kutlwano told me at the time
OL,8,Fthat his dream was to go to university
OL,9,Fto study physiotherapy and to find a
OL,10,Fway to combine it with his passion for
OL,11,Ffootball.
OL,13,F"For (my parents' generation) their
OL,14,Fpoliticians were the politicians but
OL,15,Four icons are these football stars,"
OL,16,Fhe told me.
OL,18,FMeeting Kutlwano again fourteen years
OL,19,Flater, in the family's newly-extended
OL,20,Fhome, he proudly reveals he is "living
OL,21,Fhis dream".
