OL,6,FHe now works as a physiotherapist at
OL,7,FOrlando Pirates, the football team he,
OL,8,Fhis parents, and his grandfather have
OL,9,Fsupported all their lives. His newborn
OL,10,Fbaby would almost certainly become a
OL,11,F"Pirate" too.
OL,13,FKutlwano travels the world to treat
OL,14,Fthe superstar players.
OL,16,F"In 2010, I spoke about dreams and
OL,17,Fthis is me probably living the dream"
OL,18,Fhe tells me. "I never thought that I
OL,19,Fwould be a physiotherapist for a team
OL,20,FI grew up supporting - one of the
OL,21,Fbiggest football clubs in the country."
