OL,6,FKutlwano's sister, Ofentse, who as a
OL,7,Fschool pupil 14 years ago said she
OL,8,Faspired to have a leadership role in
OL,9,Fthe education system, has just been
OL,10,Fpromoted to principal at an elite
OL,11,Fschool.
OL,13,FThis week she is teaching her pupils -
OL,14,Fwhite and black - about the importance
OL,15,Fof democracy.
OL,17,F"We teach a generation that is very
OL,18,Fvocal compared to us, we teach a
OL,19,Fgeneration that is not easily
OL,20,Finfluenced into thinking a certain
OL,21,Fway."
