OL,6,FHer parents see in their family a
OL,7,Fstory of South African success.
OL,9,F"For me the ANC has worked very much,"
OL,10,Fsays their mother Nothemba.
OL,12,FShe will not forget apartheid, and
OL,13,Fcredits the ANC for helping to bring
OL,14,Fthe racist system down.
OL,16,FThe data is damning for the governing
OL,17,Fparty. But elections are won and lost
OL,18,Fon emotional connections too.
